location.fullValue: Stellar Plan, Del Webb Charleston at Nexton

data.description: Immaculately kept and just built in 2019, Del Webb Nexton's popular Martin Ray model. This home is in perfect, move-in ready condition and shows like a model home! Featuring the upgrades buyers are looking for today plus many after market improvements. Situation on a beautiful lagoon homesite with great proximity to the communities entrance and amenity center as an added bonus! A thoughtfully designed layout with 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, den/office, screen-in lanai with vinyl windows, and a 2.5 car garage with golf cart parking, extra storage, or woodworking location. A welcoming front porch sets the scene. Upon entering the home, step into a defined foyer with charming archway. Just off the foyer you will find an office/study/den with lots of natural light. Open concept living with......the kitchen open to the great room and dining area. A kitchen ready for entertaining featuring upgraded cabinetry with crown molding, pull out drawers in all lower cabinets, built-in cabinet for trash and recycling, upgraded Moen faucet, granite countertops with large center island, stainless steel gourmet appliances featuring a gas cooktop, built-in wall oven/microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator, subway tile backsplash, pendant and recessed lighting, oversized walk-in pantry with wood shelving, and butlers pantry nearby. Low maintenance laminate flooring extends throughout the entire home with ceramic tile in the bathrooms and laundry room. Outside, a screen-in lanai with vinyl windows and roll down sun shades that functions like a second great room with tranquil lagoon views. Back inside, he primary suite offers the perfect owner's retreat highlighted with lagoon views, tray ceiling, ADA approved zero entry tiled shower with seat, Quartz countertop dual vanities and sinks, and a walk-in closet with custom shelving.  The laundry room is located just outside the primary bedroom offering pure convenience. Additional storage opportunities available in the laundry room and nearby hallway walk-in closet. The second bedroom and bathroom has its own separate hallway offering guest ample privacy. From there, the owners entry with built-in drop zone takes you to a 2.5 car garage offering additional storage opportunities, golf cart parking, or woodworking workshop! Unique features include the following ADA approved modifications during construction; zero entry on all exterior doors throughout, wheelchair accessible shower, and egress primary suite. This current homeowners have an assumable VA mortgage with an interest rate of 2.25 (borrower must be eligible for a VA loan). Desirable after market improvements include; all window treatments including pull down shades and draperies, ceiling fans, custom closet shelving (removed all wire shelving), Rachio smart irrigation controller, and keyless entry. No need wait for new construction with all appliances including refrigerator, washer, and dryer conveying this home truly move-in ready. Don't miss this gorgeous home, please book your showing today!
